///
/// A simple recurrent layer.
///
/// .. code::
///
///       y_t = SimpleRecurrentLayer(x_t, y_{t-1})
///
/// Input
///     A blob of rank 5, with shape `\[Seq, Batch, inputVectorSize, 1, 1\]``.
///     This represents a sequence of vectors of size ``inputVectorSize``.
